<br />Anyone got a diogram to show a simple pinout to run from 60pin to 72pin? I got some adaptors on order but I also have some famicom games I got in the mail I just can't wait to play so I'm more than willing to solder up a quick fix unitll I get the factory made ones in the mail...lol..
